latestIgtvVideos.title: Kadhi pakoda
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Slice 1 onion and add few garlic cloves. Let the onions turn pink then sprinkle water. Cover and cook for few minutes until it turns soft then mash it with the help of spoon

In your mixer add 3 cups yoghurt, 1 cup gram flour, 1 tsp turmeric, 2 tsp red chili powder, 1 tbsp coriander powder and mix it. Add this mixture into the pan and Add 6 cups water. Stir continuously on medium high flame until kadhi comes to a boil. Then lower the heat to low medium and let it cook for 1 hour or more until it gets thick. Keep stirring in between. 

Pakoda mixture:
To a large bowl add sliced potatoes and onion 
Add 1 tsp salt, 1 tsp red chili powder, crushed coriander and cumin 1 tsp, dry fenugreek 1 tbsp, baking soda 1/2 tsp, chili flakes 1 tsp, gram flour, spinach, green chilies and mix by adding water. 

Heat oil in a kadai to fry the pakodas. Start dropping the batter into the hot oil. Let it cook and turn golden brown from one side and the. Flip and cook the other side. Add pakoday into the kadhi 

Tadka: 
Once the oil is hot add 1 tsp cumin seeds, 1 tsp mustard seeds, whole red chilies, curry leaves, green chili, red chili powder 
Pour tadka over kadhi and garnish with fresh chopped coriander.
Serve kadhi pakoda with rice.
